'''''Condannato a nozze'''''  (also known as ''Diary of a Man Condemned to Marriage'')  is a 1993 [[Cinema of Italy|Italian]] [[comedy film]] directed by [[Giuseppe Piccioni]].<ref name="90 L">{{cite book|author1=Roberto Chiti |author2=Enrico Lancia |author3=Roberto Poppi |title=Dizionario del cinema italiano: I Film|publisher=Gremese Editore, 2002|isbn=}}</ref><ref name=Mereghetti>{{cite book|last=Paolo Mereghetti|title=Il Mereghetti|publisher=B.C. Dalai Editore, 2010|isbn=8860736269}}</ref> It entered the Panorama section at the [[50th Venice International Film Festival]].<ref>{{cite news|last=David Rooney|title=Young filmers shape slim Panorama|url=https://variety.com/1993/film/news/young-filmers-shape-slim-panorama-110132/|accessdate=25 April 2014|newspaper=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=September 6, 1993}}</ref>

